{"tid":2406232,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"傳媒稱中國拒向世衛提供疫情早期個案原始個人數據","createTime":"2021-02-13T04:41:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-14T11:32:59.000Z","uid":79563,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"689abdf9b8e670f4fac81f11b8a35a2f6e354e67","tid":2406232,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T04:41:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1575504-20210213.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1575504-20210213.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=kdQtjCisvz5VKkzPdH2zQ4uQyocENDzUuJTHoiHzCac%3D&h=b97caf67\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1575504-20210213.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=1870cb8c\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1575504-20210213.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n華爾街日報報道，中國拒絕向世界衛生組織提供早期新型肺炎個案的原始個人數據。<br />\n<br />\n報道表示，部分世衛調查員曾經因為缺乏數據的詳細內容而出現激烈的對話。報道又引述一名世衛人員表示，原始的個人數據有助理解新型冠狀病毒在中國傳播的時間及情況。"},{"pid":"eb36bfe4aa20f7c58dd7b7baac028e876f61886b","tid":2406232,"uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T04:50:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2635000/2638906/0509002_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2635000%2F2638906%2F0509002_1024.jpg&h=149fa79d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f6a9aa84669a5f402983f74af0fbc5818d07faaf","tid":2406232,"uid":205927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T04:51:22.000Z","msg":"身有屎"},{"pid":"7d0397d1a63df5c72a4a4c09cc037491d40b165e","tid":2406232,"uid":35112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T04:52:10.000Z","msg":"爆咗差唔多年幾兩年先去查<br />\n查條毛咩"},{"pid":"38aaf6e78ef3fcea148e05a7dd0134af4013a4e8","tid":2406232,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,